The paper discusses the evaluation of camouflage design using image similarity comparison, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of computer design for camouflage pattern design, which could fall under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. The use of algorithms for background color edge extraction suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper's emphasis on objectively evaluating camouflage design suggests a focus on machine learning and data analysis (cs.LG).
